title: Ebro In The Morning - Rest In Peace Takeoff; Migos Member Shot In Houston
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 11/1/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about the tragic death of Takeoff in Houston, last minute invites, and Elon Musk owning Twitter.

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
